	Welcome to the assessment starter package! 🎉🎉🎉

	There are three main files that you must include in your app:
		- requirements.txt --> list of required pip modules
		- lambda_function.py --> keep the same name for this file. This file contains all the triggers that are available for you to use in your assessment app. 
       		- package_ef_app.py --> This file contains the packaging script for your app. Learn more here: https://docs.eightfold.ai/app-platform-basics/packaging-your-app 

    	You can utilize this starter package as a boilerplate for your assessment integration with Eightfold. To learn more about the Eightfold developer platform, read the app platform docs: https://docs.eightfold.ai/sdk-main
